                        </foliation>
                        <condition key="good"/>
                     </supportDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote xml:id="d1">
                        <desc>1 full-page miniature of a holy person, fol. 1v; Ḥarag, fol. 2r, 77v, 84v, 86v
                           
                        </desc>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions><list><item xml:id="a1">Texts in a secondary hand: Commentary on Fekkārē Iyasus, front flyleaf and fol. 1r, 98v; Medical prescriptions, fol. 97rv; Synaxarion entry for Saint Roch as a prayer against plague, fol. 97v-98r; Fidal of the labiovelar consonants, fol. 98r</item><item xml:id="e1">Owned by ወልደ፡ ዮሐንስ, fol. 92v, 93v, 97r; Text on flyleaf copied for ገብረ፡ ጻድቅ, recto of front flyleaf; Seal of the Institute of Ethiopian Studies, fol. 1r
                     
                  </item></list></additions>
               </physDesc>
               <history>
